  <description>NutchWAX is 
  &lt;i&gt;
  "&lt;a href="http://nutch.org"&gt;Nutch&lt;/a&gt; Web Archive eXtensions"
  &lt;/i&gt;.  Nutch + NutchWAX can be used search Web Archive Collections
  (WACs).  Extensions include adaptation of the Nutch fetcher step to go
  against web archives rather than open net. Index-time and
  query-time plugins
  add to the index and allow querying of a records' WAC
  location info., collection name, etc.  This project is sponsored by the
  &lt;a href="http://netpreserve.org"&gt;International Internet Preservation
  Consortium&lt;/a&gt;.
  </description>
  <!-- a short description of what the project does -->
  <shortDescription>Nutch Web Archive eXtensions
  </shortDescription>
